  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your primal savagery grants you the following benefits:</p><p><strong>Savage Physical Defense:</strong> You gain access to the following <strong>PD </strong>formula while not wearing Armor:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>8 + Combat Mastery + (Might or Agility) + Prime.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p><strong>Fast Movement:</strong> You gain +1 Speed while not wearing Armor.</p><p><strong>Mighty Leap: </strong>You can use your Might instead of Agility to determine your Jump Distance and the damage you take from Falling.</p><p> </p><p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can select \"Savage Defence\" on Physical Defence Configuration on your Character sheet. You can select \"Might\" as a Jump Attribute on Jump Configuration on your Character sheet.</em></p>",
